flowchart TD
    Browser[Browser multipart upload] --> Route[Flask upload route]
    Route --> Auth[Login and company access check]
    Auth --> Staging[Write temporary staging file]
    Staging --> Validate[Validate size, extension, MIME signature]
    Validate --> Hash[Calculate SHA256]
    Hash --> Dedupe{Existing file for company}
    Dedupe -- Yes --> Existing[Reuse existing EvidenceFile]
    Dedupe -- No --> Store[Move file to local storage]
    Store --> Record[Create EvidenceFile pending]
    Record --> ProcessJob[Start processing job]
    Existing --> Link[Link to Data Entry row if requested]
    ProcessJob --> Link
    Link --> Response[Return upload result]
